mol modstyle 0 0 CPK
color Display Background white
axes location Off
mol color Name
mol representation CPK 1.000000 0.300000 12.000000 10.000000
mol selection all
mol material Opaque

# show the first molecule in normal colors
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 0 0 index <= 4

# show zeroth eigenvector in a special color (only largest absolute values)
mol modselect 1 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 1 0 ColorID 5
mol drawframes 0 1 {REPLACE00}


# first eigenvector positive and negative
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 2 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 2 0 ColorID 0
mol drawframes 0 2 {REPLACE01}
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 3 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 3 0 ColorID 1
mol drawframes 0 3 {REPLACE02}

# second eigenvector positive and negative
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 4 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 4 0 ColorID 0
mol drawframes 0 4 {REPLACE03}
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 5 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 5 0 ColorID 1
mol drawframes 0 5 {REPLACE04}

# third eigenvector positive and negative
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 6 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 6 0 ColorID 0
mol drawframes 0 6 {REPLACE05}
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 7 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 7 0 ColorID 1
mol drawframes 0 7 {REPLACE06}


# fourth eigenvector positive and negative
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 8 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 8 0 ColorID 0
mol drawframes 0 8 {REPLACE07}
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 9 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 9 0 ColorID 1
mol drawframes 0 9 {REPLACE08}

# fifth eigenvector positive and negative
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 10 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 10 0 ColorID 0
mol drawframes 0 10 {REPLACE09}
mol addrep 0
mol modselect 11 0 index > 4
mol modcolor 11 0 ColorID 1
mol drawframes 0 11 {REPLACE10}

